0 -12 Td
(files directly into the model. Instead, it validates that a file is a Windows PE file, ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(extracts the exact 2381 numerical PE features expected by the trained model, scores those ) Tj
0 -12 Td
(features with a pre-trained LightGBM model, applies policy thresholds, and emits a JSON event.) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
