(For a single file, the lifecycle is:) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(```text) Tj
0 -12 Td
(1. CLI or caller passes a file path) Tj
0 -12 Td
(2. Scanner loads policy and model package) Tj
0 -12 Td
(3. Scanner checks whether scanning is enabled) Tj
0 -12 Td
