0 -12 Td
/F1 9 Tf
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(Recommended handoff sequence:) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(1. Agent receives or observes a file path.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(2. Agent calls scanner module or executable with that path.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(3. Scanner returns JSON.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(4. Agent records telemetry.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(5. Agent decides whether to enforce action based on policy and `decision.action`.) Tj
0 -12 Td
(6. Agent handles any quarantine/delete/block behavior outside scanner v1.) Tj
0 -12 Td
() Tj
0 -12 Td
(This keeps the ML scanner small, inspectable, and focused on inference.) Tj
